eriRouterPvcMib.name: eriRouterPvcMib

revisions.description: Updated RBN/rbn/Rbn as ERICSSON-ROUTER/eriRouter/EriRouter to migrate RBN MIB to ERICSSON MIB.
Added new encaps type to TEXTUAL-CONVENTION EriRouterAtmEncapsulation.
Added new encaps type to TEXTUAL-CONVENTION EriRouterFrameRelayEncapsulation. Added new encaps type to TEXTUAL-CONVENTION EriRouterAtmEncapsulation.

The following changes were made to manage the configuration of 802.1Q PVCs on Ethernet ports, ATM circuits and Frame Relay circuits: Updated MODULE-IDENTITY. Added TEXTUAL-CONVENTION EriRouterDot1qEncapsulation. Added three new tables: eriRouterDot1qPvcOnEthConfigTable eriRouterDot1qPvcOnAtmConfigTable eriRouterDot1qPvcOnFrConfigTable Added new compliance module and groups: eriRouterPvcCompliance3 eriRouterDot1qPvcOnEthGroup eriRouterDot1qPvcOnAtmGroup eriRouterDot1qPvcOnFrGroup

To support categorization of circuit types, to provide an object to link entries in the eriRouterAtmPvcConfigTable and the eriRouterFrameRelayPvcConfigTable to the eriRouterBindTable from the ERICSSON-ROUTER-BIND-MIB, and to provide the capability to clear subscribers from circuits, witness the following changes: Updated MODULE-IDENTITY. Added TEXTUAL-CONVENTION EriRouterPvcCircuitType. Added new objects to eriRouterAtmPvcConfigTable: eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitHandle eriRouterAtmPvcClearCircuit Added new objects to eriRouterFrameRelayPvcConfigTable: eriRouterFrameRelayPvcCircuitType eriRouterFrameRelayPvcCircuitHandle eriRouterFrameRelayPvcClearCircuit Added new MODULE-COMPLIANCE and OBJECT-GROUPs: eriRouterPvcCompliance2 eriRouterAtmPvcGroup2 eriRouterFrameRelayPvcGroup2
Moved EriRouterSlot and EriRouterPort definitions to Textual Convention MIB (ERICSSON-ROUTER-TC).
Updated CONTACT-INFO clause in MODULE-IDENTITY. Added new CLIPs encaps type to the EriRouterFrameRelayEncapsulation and EriRouterAtmEncapsulation TEXTUAL-CONVENTION definitions.
Updated range on EriRouterSlot, EriRouterPort, and eriRouterAtmPvcVpi.
Removed all references to padding which was an obsoleted attribute of PVC circuits.

eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType.name: eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType
eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType.description: The PVC circuit type. With respect to this mib object, only those entries whose eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType has a value 'explicit' may be removed by setting eriRouterAtmPvcRowStatus equal to 'destroy'. A set operation with eriRouterAtmPvcRowStatus equal to 'destroy' on any row with eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitType not equal to 'explicit' will result in an INCONSISTENT_VALUE_ERROR.

eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitHandle.name: eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitHandle
eriRouterAtmPvcCircuitHandle.description: This object is used internally to uniquely identify a circuit. The value of this object may be used to correlate entries with those in the eriRouterBindTable defined in the ERICSSON-ROUTER-BIND-MIB.

eriRouterAtmPvcClearCircuit.name: eriRouterAtmPvcClearCircuit
eriRouterAtmPvcClearCircuit.description: When this object is true(1), the system will clear active subscriber sessions on the specified circuit. When false(2), there is no action taken. This object can only be written when the conceptual row exists. When this object is set to true(1) and the encapsulation of the circuit is bridged or routed, e.g. bridge1483(2) or route1483(4), subscribers will re-authenticate after being cleared.
